product_name: IT CosmeticsBrow Power Universal Eyebrow Pencil
summary: SummaryIT Cosmetics Brow Power Universal Eyebrow Pencil is a longwear, brow pencil that transforms to any hair color for the appearance of natural brows.
details: DetailsBenefitsUniversal Taupe shade adjusts to your eyebrow color based on pressure applied to make penciling in your eyebrows easyLongwear eyebrow pencil formula adheres to skin for the appearance of full brows that lastBuilt-in spoolie brush delivers a natural, polished look to arched browsFeatures brow enhancer ingredients including biotin, lecithin, grape seed, saw palmetto, green tea and antioxidantsKey IngredientsBiotin: B vitamin that supports stronger, healthier-looking hair and skinSaw Palmetto: A plant extract that conditions your skin and promotes stronger-looking hairItem 2568656How To UseUse softer strokes for lighter hair colors including blonde and gray. Press harder for darker tones including brown and black. Finish by lightly brushing the built-in spooley brush through your brows for a natural, polished look.To create your most perfect-looking eyebrows:The start of your brows should line up directly with the edge of your nose.Your brow arch should align to the outer edge of your iris.The end of your brow line should line up with the outer corner of your eye.IngredientsHydrogenated Coco-Glycerides, Ceresin, Candelilla Cera/Euphorbia Cerifera (Candelilla) Wax/Cire De Candelilla, Cera Carnauba/Copernicia Cerifera (Carnauba) Wax/Cire De Carnauba, Cera Alba/Beeswax/Cire D'abeille, Cera Microcristallina/Microcrystalline Wax/Cire Microcristalline, Tocopheryl Acetate, BHT, Serenoa Serrulata Fruit Extract, Biotin, Urtica Dioica (Nettle) Leaf Powder, Equisetum Arvense Extract, Lecithin, Pantothenic Acid, Camellia Sinensis Leaf Extract, Vitis Vinifera (Grape) Seed Extract, Ascorbic Acid, Retinyl Acetate, Iron Oxides(CI 77492, CI 77499, CI 77491).Shipping & Coupon RestrictionsThis brand is excluded from most Ulta Beauty coupons.See brand eligibility details
how_to_use: Use softer strokes for lighter hair colors including blonde and gray. Press harder for darker tones including brown and black. Finish by lightly brushing the built-in spooley brush through your brows for a natural, polished look.To create your most perfect-looking eyebrows:The start of your brows should line up directly with the edge of your nose.Your brow arch should align to the outer edge of your iris.The end of your brow line should line up with the outer corner of your eye.

faceoff_positive.comments: I am a breast cancer survivor. During treatment I was invited to a Look Good Feel Better event. I had no hair, eyelashes or eyebrows and was feeling very sorry for myself. One of the products included was Brow Power, a miracle for me. Doing my makeup and sharing a laugh with other cancer patients was so helpful for me. I continue to use Brow Power and other IT products and I love them. Thank you Jamie.
faceoff_positive.headline: Love Brow Power!!!

faceoff_negative.comments: The selling point for this product is that it is universal for all eyebrow hair colors. NOT TRUE! The instructions say to press harder to fill in the brows of dark brown or black users. If you do that, the end result isn't natural at all! Even using the eyebrow brush smudger doesn't make it look natural. It takes off the color. It also gives your dk brown brows an "ashey" tone. The harder you press to create a darker color, the more you look like a "painted lady". You know those ladies...the "drawn on eyebrow" look. I would only recommend this product for users with light brown eyebrow hair.
faceoff_negative.headline: Don't "buy into" the hype!!
